description: This fully renovated three-story residence offers the perfect blend of city convenience and modern comfort. It features 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and 2 private outdoor spaces. The main living level boasts an open-concept layout flooded with natural light, connecting the kitchen, dining, and living areas. The chef’s kitchen includes stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, and a Carrara marble herringbone backsplash. The top floor is dedicated to a primary suite, complete with a walk-in closet, full bathroom, and private roof deck offering city views. The second level includes 2 spacious bedrooms, a full bathroom, and a cozy nook ideal for a home office/reading area. Located just 2 blocks from the highly anticipated Washington Village development, this home offers both comfort and investment potential in one of Southie's most desirable neighborhoods.
